### 登录测试
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 注册测试
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "email": "test2@pet.com",
  "realName": "测试用户2"
}

### 用户列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/list

### 发布宠物（需要登录后获取token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pets/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小花",
  "species": "猫",
  "breed": "橘猫",
  "age": 12,
  "gender": "母",
  "weight": 3.5,
  "color": "橘色",
  "healthStatus": "健康",
  "description": "一只温顺可爱的橘猫，喜欢晒太阳",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/cat.jpg",
  "shelterId": 1
}

### 宠物列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pets/list

### 宠物详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pets/1

### 提交领养申请
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoptions/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": 1,
  "homeEnvironment": "小区楼房，三室一厅，有阳台",
  "experience": "以前养过一只猫，有3年养宠经验",
  "reason": "非常喜欢小花，希望能给她一个温暖的家"
}

### 查询我的申请记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/adoptions/my